name: Japanese Robot Birthday Greeting Card
description:
The whole Botodesigns family wishes you a happy birthday!

The Japanese says "Omedetou Gozaimasu!" which means Happy Birthday. Inside the card: "Omedetou Gozaimasu/Happy Birthday!"

Art card digitally designed. Printed on high-quality card stock with a glossy finish. Includes envelope and comes in a protective plastic sleeve. Measures 4" x 5".

Please let me know if you'd like more than 1 card.

Shipped via First Class USPS.

© 2010 Chen Reichert

name: oHanami - Japanese Cherry Blossom Picnic - 5x5 Art Print
description:
It's a beautiful day to enjoy a picnic beneath the blossoming cherry trees. An oHanami (flower viewing) is not complete without a bento, sake, cherry blossom ice cream and a blue tarp.

Can be shown alone or with the rest of the Botos' Favorite Season Set.

This is a print of my original painting. Printed with archival inks on  high quality archival matte paper.

Print measures 5X5 inches with a 1/2 inch white border for framing. It's signed, titled, dated and shipped in a cello sleeve with sturdy backing via First Class USPS shipping.

Please note: The colors seen on your monitor may vary slightly from print.

© 2010 Chen Reichert / Botodesigns
